<#tt0066050-artthethird>
	schema:about <#tt0066050>;
	schema:author "artthethird";
	schema:dateCreated "Sat Oct 26 2002 00:00:00 GMT+0200 (Mitteleuropäische Sommerzeit)";
	schema:reviewRating 7;
	schema:headline " James Garner as you've never seen him before!";
	schema:reviewBody "If nothing else can be said about it A Man Called Sledge is a slightly above average spaghetti western. It boasts James Garnerplaying against type as Luther Sledge a brutal robber who gets involved in a plot to steal a shipment of gold stored in a prison.It's a departure from his usual easygoing roles and he gets good support from TV western stars Dennis WeaverClaude Akinsand Wayde Preston. It's also directed by veteran TV actor Vic Morrow. It's okayoverall and worth a look the next time it comes on TV.".

