<#tt0066050-henry8_3>
	schema:about <#tt0066050>;
	schema:author "henry8_3";
	schema:dateCreated "Tue Mar 16 2021 00:00:00 GMT+0100 (Mitteleuropäische Normalzeit)";
	schema:reviewRating 3;
	schema:headline " A Man Called Sledge";
	schema:reviewBody "Spaghetti western with Garner atypically cast as a wanted bad guy who heads a vicious gang out to steal gold held in a top prison.It's always a pleasure to watch the great James Garner however this is stretching things to the limit. He is miscast in this ridiculous western which is just about bearable until about three quarters of the way through when the plot takes a series of bizarre turns starting with a long and daft plot devise montage section looking at the dangers of gambling and then hues downhill from there. Utterly stupid.".

