<#tt0119349-jacobmhoff>
	schema:about <#tt0119349>;
	schema:author "jacobmhoff";
	schema:dateCreated "Sat Dec 28 2019 00:00:00 GMT+0100 (Mitteleuropäische Normalzeit)";
	schema:reviewRating 10;
	schema:headline " One of the greatest.";
	schema:reviewBody "This film is a full blown masterpiece. The rating is currently 7.4  which is just sad this film should easily be on the top 250 and regarded for what it is brilliant cinema.I won't review the content of this film I mean why? It's an experience you just need to have. It's a human experience not just a pretty picture a slice of life that could only really be compared to other masterworks like Death Of A Salesman or Tolstoy. There is a universal human bond to this film that will keep it relevant forever.The direction I mean my God. The acting tone writing pacing its all in a league of its own.".

